videos.description: Tyler Goodson takes the handoff and scores a 10-yard Iowa touchdown after breaking a tackle and steamrolling a defender at the goal line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Goodson bulldozes defender to score Iowa TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Goodson bulldozes defender to score Iowa TD

videos.description: The Hawkeyes take an early 6-0 lead over the Golden Gophers as Nate Stanley completes a pass to Nico Ragaini for a 21-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stanley connects with Ragaini for 21-yard Iowa TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanley connects with Ragaini for 21-yard Iowa TD

videos.description: Tanner Morgan connects with Tyler Johnson in stride as he reaches the end zone to score a 28-yard touchdown for the Golden Gophers.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Morgan hits Johnson in stride for 28-yard Minnesota TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morgan hits Johnson in stride for 28-yard Minnesota TD

videos.description: Rodney Smith punches it in from the one-yard line score to cut Minnesota's deficit vs. Iowa to 23-19 in the fourth quarter.
